== AWS Stack Summary

* **Networking and Security**: {{https://aws.amazon.com/vpc/}Amazon VPC} creates an isolated network environment with NAT Gateway, NACLs, and VPC Flow Logs. {{https://docs.aws.amazon.com/vpc/latest/privatelink/}VPC Endpoints} provide private access to AWS services (e.g., S3, EC2, SSM), {{https://aws.amazon.com/waf/}AWS WAF} protects against web attacks, {{https://aws.amazon.com/iam/}AWS IAM} secures access control, and {{https://aws.amazon.com/kms/}AWS KMS} encrypts data at rest.

